(
  'Looking Ahead: Jazeerat Al Hadeed in 2027',
  'looking-ahead-jazeerat-2027',
  'Our strategic vision for expanding capacity, adopting new technologies, and serving the growing MENA infrastructure market.',
  '<h1>Building Capacity for the Future</h1><p>As the GCC continues its rapid infrastructure expansion, driven by initiatives like Saudi Vision 2030 and UAE Net Zero 2050, the demand for high-quality structural steel has never been higher. At Jazeerat Al Hadeed, we are not just keeping pace; we are building capacity for the future.</p><h2>Expansion Plans</h2><p>Our strategic roadmap for 2027 includes a 30% expansion of our covered fabrication area, the installation of a new fully automated shot-blasting and painting line, and a targeted recruitment drive for advanced BIM detailers.</p><p>We remain committed to our core philosophy: delivering complex steel structures on time, on budget, and with uncompromising quality.</p>',
